                            <comment id="12780914" author="stack" created="Sat, 21 Nov 2009 05:40:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is particular noticeable when the upload is done out of map tasks.  The task creates an HTable and then exits when done, perhaps thousands of times.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The idea to register a shutdown hooks was J-Ds.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12780915" author="stack" created="Sat, 21 Nov 2009 05:41:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh, and I think J-Ds idea of a shutdown hook a good one. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12781081" author="stack" created="Sun, 22 Nov 2009 01:38:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch seems to do the right thing.  I tried it in a MR context and I see closeSession instead of expiredSession in zk logs when its in place.  Task logs look fine too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12781097" author="jdcryans" created="Sun, 22 Nov 2009 06:06:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12781251" author="stack" created="Sun, 22 Nov 2009 23:36:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied branch and trunk (Thanks for review J-D).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
